b:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both IFTTT and n8n share a solid foundation of core features including Visual Builder, Api Connections, Scheduling, Conditional Logic. On the other hand, n8n uniquely offers Code Support and Error Handling and Team Collaboration, giving it an edge for users who prioritize these areas. \n\nLooking at user ratings, IFTTT holds an overall score of 6/10 and an ease of use score of 10/10, while n8n scores 8/10 overall and 6/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
c:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, both IFTTT and n8n offer flexible pricing models. Both platforms offer free plans, which is great for testing before committing. IFTTT's free tier and n8n's free tier each have their own limitations, so it is worth evaluating both to see which free offering better matches your initial needs."}]]}]
